8.87103 20 10.4177 20 12C20 14.1217 19.1572 16.1566 17.6569 17.6569C16.1566 19.1571 14.1217 20 12 20Z"></path></svg>Note</p><div class="starlight-aside__content"><p>The <code dir="auto">.opencode</code> and <code dir="auto">~/.config/opencode</code> directories use <strong>plural names</strong> for subdirectories: <code dir="auto">agents/</code>, <code dir="auto">commands/</code>, <code dir="auto">modes/</code>, <code dir="auto">plugins/</code>, <code dir="auto">skills/</code>, <code dir="auto">tools/</code>, and <code dir="auto">themes/</code>. Singular names (e.g., <code dir="auto">agent/</code>) are also supported for backwards compatibility.</p></div></aside>
