266:<h3 id="plugins"><a href="#plugins">Plugins</a></h3>
267:<p><a href="/docs/plugins">Plugins</a> extend OpenCode with custom tools, hooks, and integrations.</p>
268:<p>Place plugin files in <code dir="auto">.opencode/plugins/</code> or <code dir="auto">~/.config/opencode/plugins/</code>. You can also load plugins from npm through the <code dir="auto">plugin</code> option.</p>
270:<p><a href="/docs/plugins">Learn more here</a>.</p>
